var book = {
	"name": "Mark",
	"numChapters": 16,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The beginning of the gospel of Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24213A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24213A\"></sup>the Son of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24214B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24214B\"></sup>As it is written in Isaiah the prophet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24214C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24214C\"></sup>“Behold, I send my messenger before your face,who will prepare your way,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24215D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24215D\"></sup>the voice of one crying in the wilderness:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24215E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24215E\"></sup>‘Prepare the way of the Lord,make his paths straight,’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24216F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24216F\"></sup>John appeared, baptizing in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24216G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24216G\"></sup>the wilderness and proclaiming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24216H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24216H\"></sup>a baptism of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24216I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24216I\"></sup>repentance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24216J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24216J\"></sup>for the forgiveness of sins.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And all the country of Judea and all Jerusalem were going out to him and were being baptized by him in the river Jordan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24217K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24217K\"></sup>confessing their sins.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now John was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24218L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24218L\"></sup>clothed with camel's hair and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24218M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24218M\"></sup>wore a leather belt around his waist and ate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24218N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24218N\"></sup>locusts and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24218O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24218O\"></sup>wild honey.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he preached, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24219P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24219P\"></sup>“After me comes he who is mightier than I, the strap of whose sandals I am not worthy to stoop down and untie.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24220Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24220Q\"></sup>I have baptized you with water, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24220R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24220R\"></sup>he will baptize you with the Holy Spirit.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24221S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24221S\"></sup>In those days Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24221T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24221T\"></sup>came from Nazareth of Galilee and was baptized by John in the Jordan.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And when he came up out of the water, immediately he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24222U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24222U\"></sup>saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24222V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24222V\"></sup>the heavens being torn open <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24222W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24222W\"></sup>and the Spirit descending on him like a dove.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24223X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24223X\"></sup>a voice came from heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24223Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24223Y\"></sup>“You are my beloved Son; with you I am well pleased.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24224Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24224Z\"></sup>The Spirit immediately drove him out into the wilderness.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24225AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24225AA\"></sup>And he was in the wilderness forty days, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24225AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24225AB\"></sup>tempted by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24225AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24225AC\"></sup>Satan. And he was with the wild animals, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24225AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24225AD\"></sup>the angels were ministering to him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24226AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24226AE\"></sup>Now after John was arrested, Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24226AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24226AF\"></sup>came into Galilee, proclaiming the gospel of God,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24227AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24227AG\"></sup>“The time is fulfilled, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24227AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24227AH\"></sup>the kingdom of God is at hand; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24227AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24227AI\"></sup>repent and believe in the gospel.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24228AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24228AJ\"></sup>Passing alongside the Sea of Galilee, he saw Simon and Andrew the brother of Simon casting a net into the sea, for they were fishermen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me, and I will make you become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24229AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24229AK\"></sup>fishers of men.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And immediately they left their nets and followed him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And going on a little farther, he saw James the son of Zebedee and John his brother, who were in their boat mending the nets.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And immediately he called them, and they left their father Zebedee in the boat with the hired servants and followed him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24233AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24233AL\"></sup>And they went into Capernaum, and immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24233AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24233AM\"></sup>on the Sabbath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24233AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24233AN\"></sup>he entered the synagogue and was teaching.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24234AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24234AO\"></sup>they were astonished at his teaching, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24234AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24234AP\"></sup>for he taught them as one who had authority, and not as the scribes.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And immediately there was in their synagogue a man with an unclean spirit. And he cried out,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24236AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24236AQ\"></sup>“What have you to do with us, Jesus of Nazareth? Have you come to destroy us? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24236AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24236AR\"></sup>I know who you are—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24236AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24236AS\"></sup>the Holy One of God.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24237AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24237AT\"></sup>rebuked him, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Be silent, and come out of him!”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And the unclean spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24238AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24238AU\"></sup>convulsing him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24238AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24238AV\"></sup>crying out with a loud voice, came out of him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24239AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24239AW\"></sup>amazed, so that they questioned among themselves, saying, “What is this? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24239AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24239AX\"></sup>A new teaching with authority! He commands even the unclean spirits, and they obey him.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And at once his fame spread everywhere throughout all the surrounding region of Galilee.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24241AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24241AY\"></sup>And immediately he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24241AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24241AZ\"></sup>left the synagogue and entered the house of Simon and Andrew, with James and John.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24242BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24242BA\"></sup>Simon's mother-in-law lay ill with a fever, and immediately they told him about her.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And he came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24243BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24243BB\"></sup>took her by the hand and lifted her up, and the fever left her, and she began to serve them.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>That evening at sundown they brought to him all who were sick or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24244BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24244BC\"></sup>oppressed by demons.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And the whole city was gathered together at the door.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24246BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24246BD\"></sup>And he healed many who were sick with various diseases, and cast out many demons. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24246BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24246BE\"></sup>he would not permit the demons to speak, because they knew him.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24247BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24247BF\"></sup>And rising very early in the morning, while it was still dark, he departed and went out to a desolate place, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24247BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24247BG\"></sup>there he prayed.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And Simon and those who were with him searched for him,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>and they found him and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24249BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24249BH\"></sup>“Everyone is looking for you.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Let us go on to the next towns, that I may preach there also, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24250BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24250BI\"></sup>that is why I came out.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24251BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24251BJ\"></sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24251BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24251BK\"></sup>he went throughout all Galilee, preaching in their synagogues and casting out demons.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24252BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24252BL\"></sup>And a leper came to him, imploring him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24252BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24252BM\"></sup>kneeling said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24252BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24252BN\"></sup>“If you will, you can make me clean.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Moved with pity, he stretched out his hand and touched him and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I will; be clean.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And immediately the leprosy left him, and he was made clean.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24255BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24255BO\"></sup>Jesus sternly charged him and sent him away at once,",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>and said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24256BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24256BP\"></sup>“See that you say nothing to anyone, but go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24256BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24256BQ\"></sup>show yourself to the priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24256BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24256BR\"></sup>offer for your cleansing what Moses commanded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24256BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24256BS\"></sup>for a proof to them.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24257BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24257BT\"></sup>But he went out and began to talk freely about it, and to spread the news, so that Jesus could no longer openly enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24257BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24257BU\"></sup>a town, but was out in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24257BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24257BV\"></sup>desolate places, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24257BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24257BW\"></sup>people were coming to him from every quarter."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>And when he returned to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24258A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24258A\"></sup>Capernaum after some days, it was reported that he was at home.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And many were gathered together, so that there was no more room, not even at the door. And he was preaching the word to them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24260B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24260B\"></sup>And they came, bringing to him a paralytic carried by four men.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when they could not get near him because of the crowd, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24261C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24261C\"></sup>they removed the roof above him, and when they had made an opening, they let down the bed on which the paralytic lay.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24262D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24262D\"></sup>saw their faith, he said to the paralytic, <span class=\"woj\">“Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24262E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24262E\"></sup>your sins are forgiven.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now some of the scribes were sitting there, questioning in their hearts,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Why does this man speak like that? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24264F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24264F\"></sup>He is blaspheming! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24264G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24264G\"></sup>Who can forgive sins but God alone?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And immediately Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24265H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24265H\"></sup>perceiving in his spirit that they thus questioned within themselves, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you question these things in your hearts?</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Which is easier, to say to the paralytic, ‘Your sins are forgiven,’ or to say, ‘Rise, take up your bed and walk’?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24267I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24267I\"></sup>the Son of Man has authority on earth to forgive sins”</span>—he said to the paralytic—",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I say to you, rise, pick up your bed, and go home.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And he rose and immediately picked up his bed and went out before them all, so that they were all amazed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24269J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24269J\"></sup>glorified God, saying, “We never saw anything like this!”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He went out again beside the sea, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24270K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24270K\"></sup>all the crowd was coming to him, and he was teaching them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24271L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24271L\"></sup>And as he passed by, he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24271M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24271M\"></sup>Levi the son of Alphaeus sitting at the tax booth, and he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me.”</span> And he rose and followed him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And as he reclined at table in his house, many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24272N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24272N\"></sup>tax collectors and sinners were reclining with Jesus and his disciples, for there were many who followed him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24273O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24273O\"></sup>the scribes of the Pharisees, when they saw that he was eating with sinners and tax collectors, said to his disciples, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24273P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24273P\"></sup>“Why does he eat with tax collectors and sinners?”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And when Jesus heard it, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Those who are well have no need of a physician, but those who are sick. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24274Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24274Q\"></sup>I came not to call the righteous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24274R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24274R\"></sup>but sinners.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24275S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24275S\"></sup>John's disciples and the Pharisees were fasting. And people came and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24275T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24275T\"></sup>“Why do John's disciples and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24275U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24275U\"></sup>the disciples of the Pharisees fast, but your disciples do not fast?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24276V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24276V\"></sup>“Can the wedding guests fast while the bridegroom is with them? As long as they have the bridegroom with them, they cannot fast.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24277W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24277W\"></sup>The days will come when the bridegroom is taken away from them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24277X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24277X\"></sup>then they will fast in that day.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>No one sews a piece of unshrunk cloth on an old garment. If he does, the patch tears away from it, the new from the old, and a worse tear is made.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And no one puts new wine into old <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24279Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24279Y\"></sup>wineskins. If he does, the wine will burst the skins—and the wine is destroyed, and so are the skins. But new wine is for fresh wineskins.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24280Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24280Z\"></sup>One Sabbath he was going through the grainfields, and as they made their way, his disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24280AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24280AA\"></sup>began to pluck heads of grain.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And the Pharisees were saying to him, “Look, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24281AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24281AB\"></sup>why are they doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24281AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24281AC\"></sup>what is not lawful on the Sabbath?”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24282AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24282AD\"></sup>“Have you never read <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24282AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24282AE\"></sup>what David did, when he was in need and was hungry, he and those who were with him:</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>how he entered the house of God, in the time of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24283AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24283AF\"></sup>Abiathar the high priest, and ate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24283AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24283AG\"></sup>the bread of the Presence, which it is not lawful for any but the priests to eat, and also gave it to those who were with him?”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24284AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24284AH\"></sup>“The Sabbath was made for man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24284AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24284AI\"></sup>not man for the Sabbath.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24285AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24285AJ\"></sup>the Son of Man is lord even of the Sabbath.”</span>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24286A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24286A\"></sup>Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24286B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24286B\"></sup>he entered the synagogue, and a man was there with a withered hand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24287C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24287C\"></sup>they watched Jesus, to see whether he would heal him on the Sabbath, so that they might accuse him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he said to the man with the withered hand, <span class=\"woj\">“Come here.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24289D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24289D\"></sup>“Is it lawful on the Sabbath to do good or to do harm, to save life or to kill?”</span> But they were silent.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24290E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24290E\"></sup>looked around at them with anger, grieved at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24290F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24290F\"></sup>their hardness of heart, and said to the man, <span class=\"woj\">“Stretch out your hand.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24290G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24290G\"></sup>He stretched it out, and his hand was restored.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24291H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24291H\"></sup>The Pharisees went out and immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24291I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24291I\"></sup>held counsel with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24291J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24291J\"></sup>the Herodians against him, how to destroy him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24292K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24292K\"></sup>Jesus withdrew with his disciples to the sea, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24292L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24292L\"></sup>a great crowd followed, from Galilee and Judea",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24293M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24293M\"></sup>Idumea and from beyond the Jordan and from around <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24293N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24293N\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon. When the great crowd heard all that he was doing, they came to him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he told his disciples to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24294O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24294O\"></sup>have a boat ready for him because of the crowd, lest they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24294P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24294P\"></sup>crush him,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24295Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24295Q\"></sup>he had healed many, so that all who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24295R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24295R\"></sup>diseases pressed around him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24295S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24295S\"></sup>to touch him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24296T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24296T\"></sup>And whenever the unclean spirits saw him, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24296U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24296U\"></sup>fell down before him and cried out, “You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24296V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24296V\"></sup>the Son of God.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24297W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24297W\"></sup>he strictly ordered them not to make him known.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24298X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24298X\"></sup>And he went up on the mountain and called to him those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24298Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24298Y\"></sup>whom he desired, and they came to him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24299Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24299Z\"></sup>And he appointed twelve (whom he also named apostles) so that they might be with him and he might send them out to preach",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24300AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24300AA\"></sup>and have authority to cast out demons.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He appointed the twelve: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24301AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24301AB\"></sup>Simon (to whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24301AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24301AC\"></sup>he gave the name Peter);",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24302AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24302AD\"></sup>James the son of Zebedee and John the brother of James (to whom he gave the name Boanerges, that is, Sons of Thunder);",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Andrew, and Philip, and Bartholomew, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24303AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24303AE\"></sup>Matthew, and Thomas, and James the son of Alphaeus, and Thaddaeus, and Simon the Zealot,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and Judas Iscariot, who betrayed him.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then he went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24305AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24305AF\"></sup>home, and the crowd gathered again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24305AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24305AG\"></sup>so that they could not even eat.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24306AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24306AH\"></sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24306AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24306AI\"></sup>his family heard it, they went out to seize him, for they were saying, “He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24306AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24306AJ\"></sup>is out of his mind.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24307AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24307AK\"></sup>the scribes who came down from Jerusalem were saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24307AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24307AL\"></sup>“He is possessed by Beelzebul,” and “by the prince of demons he casts out the demons.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24308AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24308AM\"></sup>And he called them to him and said to them in parables, <span class=\"woj\">“How can Satan cast out Satan?</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>If a kingdom is divided against itself, that kingdom cannot stand.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And if a house is divided against itself, that house will not be able to stand.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And if Satan has risen up against himself and is divided, he cannot stand, but is coming to an end.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24312AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24312AN\"></sup>no one can enter a strong man's house and plunder his goods, unless he first binds the strong man. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24312AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24312AO\"></sup>Then indeed he may plunder his house.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24313AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24313AP\"></sup>“Truly, I say to you, all sins will be forgiven the children of man, and whatever blasphemies they utter,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>but whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24314AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24314AQ\"></sup>blasphemes against the Holy Spirit never has forgiveness, but is guilty of an eternal sin”</span>—",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>for they were saying, “He has an unclean spirit.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24316AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24316AR\"></sup>And his mother and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24316AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24316AS\"></sup>brothers came, and standing outside they sent to him and called him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And a crowd was sitting around him, and they said to him, “Your mother and your brothers are outside, seeking you.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Who are my mother and my brothers?”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24319AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24319AT\"></sup>looking about at those who sat around him, he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Here are my mother and my brothers!</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24320AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24320AU\"></sup>For whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24320AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24320AV\"></sup>does the will of God, he is my brother and sister and mother.”</span>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24321A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24321A\"></sup>he began to teach beside the sea. And a very large crowd gathered about him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24321B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24321B\"></sup>so that he got into a boat and sat in it on the sea, and the whole crowd was beside the sea on the land.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24322C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24322C\"></sup>he was teaching them many things in parables, and in his teaching he said to them:",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Listen! Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24323D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24323D\"></sup>a sower went out to sow.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And as he sowed, some seed fell along the path, and the birds came and devoured it.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Other seed fell on rocky ground, where it did not have much soil, and immediately it sprang up, since it had no depth of soil.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24326E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24326E\"></sup>when the sun rose, it was scorched, and since it had no root, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24326F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24326F\"></sup>it withered away.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Other seed fell among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24327G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24327G\"></sup>thorns, and the thorns grew up and choked it, and it yielded no grain.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And other seeds fell into good soil and produced grain, growing up and increasing and yielding thirtyfold and sixtyfold and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24328H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24328H\"></sup>a hundredfold.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24329I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24329I\"></sup>“He who has ears to hear, let him hear.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24330J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24330J\"></sup>when he was alone, those around him with the twelve asked him about the parables.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24331K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24331K\"></sup>“To you has been given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24331L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24331L\"></sup>the secret of the kingdom of God, but for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24331M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24331M\"></sup>those outside everything is in parables,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24332N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24332N\"></sup>so that</span><span class=\"woj\">“‘they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24332O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24332O\"></sup>may indeed see but not perceive,</span><span class=\"woj\">and may indeed hear but not understand,</span><span class=\"woj\">lest they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24332P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24332P\"></sup>should turn and be forgiven.’”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24333Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24333Q\"></sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you not understand this parable? How then will you understand all the parables?</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24334R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24334R\"></sup>The sower sows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24334S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24334S\"></sup>the word.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And these are the ones along the path, where the word is sown: when they hear, Satan immediately comes and takes away the word that is sown in them.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And these are the ones sown on rocky ground: the ones who, when they hear the word, immediately receive it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24336T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24336T\"></sup>with joy.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they have no root in themselves, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24337U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24337U\"></sup>endure for a while; then, when tribulation or persecution arises on account of the word, immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24337V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24337V\"></sup>they fall away.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And others are the ones sown among thorns. They are those who hear the word,</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24339W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24339W\"></sup>the cares of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24339X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24339X\"></sup>the world and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24339Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24339Y\"></sup>the deceitfulness of riches and the desires for other things enter in and choke the word, and it proves unfruitful.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But those that were sown on the good soil are the ones who hear the word and accept it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24340Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24340Z\"></sup>bear fruit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24340AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24340AA\"></sup>thirtyfold and sixtyfold and a hundredfold.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24341AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24341AB\"></sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24341AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24341AC\"></sup>“Is a lamp brought in to be put under a basket, or under a bed, and not on a stand?</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24342AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24342AD\"></sup>For nothing is hidden except to be made manifest; nor is anything secret except to come to light.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24343AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24343AE\"></sup>If anyone has ears to hear, let him hear.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Pay attention to what you hear: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24344AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24344AF\"></sup>with the measure you use, it will be measured to you, and still more will be added to you.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24345AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24345AG\"></sup>For to the one who has, more will be given, and from the one who has not, even what he has will be taken away.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24346AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24346AH\"></sup>“The kingdom of God is as if a man should scatter seed on the ground.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He sleeps and rises night and day, and the seed sprouts and grows; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24347AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24347AI\"></sup>he knows not how.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The earth produces by itself, first the blade, then the ear, then the full grain in the ear.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But when the grain is ripe, at once <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24349AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24349AJ\"></sup>he puts in the sickle, because the harvest has come.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24350AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24350AK\"></sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“With what can we compare the kingdom of God, or what parable shall we use for it?</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>It is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24351AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24351AL\"></sup>a grain of mustard seed, which, when sown on the ground, is the smallest of all the seeds on earth,</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>yet when it is sown it grows up and becomes larger than all the garden plants and puts out large branches, so that the birds of the air can make nests in its shade.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24353AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24353AM\"></sup>With many such parables he spoke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24353AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24353AN\"></sup>the word to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24353AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24353AO\"></sup>as they were able to hear it.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He did not speak to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24354AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24354AP\"></sup>without a parable, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24354AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24354AQ\"></sup>privately to his own disciples he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24354AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24354AR\"></sup>explained everything.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24355AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24355AS\"></sup>On that day, when evening had come, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Let us go across to the other side.”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And leaving the crowd, they took him with them in the boat, just as he was. And other boats were with him.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And a great windstorm arose, and the waves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24357AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24357AT\"></sup>were breaking into the boat, so that the boat was already filling.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But he was in the stern, asleep on the cushion. And they woke him and said to him, “Teacher, do you not care that we are perishing?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And he awoke and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24359AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24359AU\"></sup>rebuked the wind and said to the sea, <span class=\"woj\">“Peace! Be still!”</span> And the wind ceased, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24359AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24359AV\"></sup>there was a great calm.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24360AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24360AW\"></sup>so afraid? Have you still no faith?”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And they were filled with great fear and said to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24361AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24361AX\"></sup>“Who then is this, that even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24361AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24361AY\"></sup>the wind and the sea obey him?”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24362A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24362A\"></sup>They came to the other side of the sea, to the country of the Gerasenes.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when Jesus had stepped out of the boat, immediately there met him out of the tombs a man with an unclean spirit.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24364B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24364B\"></sup>He lived among the tombs. And no one could bind him anymore, not even with a chain,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for he had often been bound with shackles and chains, but he wrenched the chains apart, and he broke the shackles in pieces. No one had the strength to subdue him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Night and day among the tombs and on the mountains he was always crying out and cutting himself with stones.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when he saw Jesus from afar, he ran and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24367C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24367C\"></sup>fell down before him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24368D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24368D\"></sup>crying out with a loud voice, he said, “What have you to do with me, Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24368E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24368E\"></sup>Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24368F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24368F\"></sup>the Most High God? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24368G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24368G\"></sup>I adjure you by God, do not torment me.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For he was saying to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Come out of the man, you unclean spirit!”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And Jesus asked him, <span class=\"woj\">“What is your name?”</span> He replied, “My name is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24370H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24370H\"></sup>Legion, for we are many.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he begged him earnestly not to send them out of the country.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now a great herd of pigs was feeding there on the hillside,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and they begged him, saying, “Send us to the pigs; let us enter them.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So he gave them permission. And the unclean spirits came out and entered the pigs; and the herd, numbering about two thousand, rushed down the steep bank into the sea and drowned in the sea.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The herdsmen fled and told it in the city and in the country. And people came to see what it was that had happened.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And they came to Jesus and saw the demon-possessed man, the one who had had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24376I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24376I\"></sup>the legion, sitting there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24376J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24376J\"></sup>clothed and in his right mind, and they were afraid.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And those who had seen it described to them what had happened to the demon-possessed man and to the pigs.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24378K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24378K\"></sup>they began to beg Jesus to depart from their region.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>As he was getting into the boat, the man who had been possessed with demons begged him that he might be with him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he did not permit him but said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go home to your friends and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24380L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24380L\"></sup>tell them how much the Lord has done for you, and how he has had mercy on you.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he went away and began to proclaim in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24381M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24381M\"></sup>the Decapolis how much Jesus had done for him, and everyone marveled.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And when Jesus had crossed again in the boat to the other side, a great crowd gathered about him, and he was beside the sea.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24383N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24383N\"></sup>Then came one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24383O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24383O\"></sup>the rulers of the synagogue, Jairus by name, and seeing him, he fell at his feet",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and implored him earnestly, saying, “My little daughter is at the point of death. Come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24384P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24384P\"></sup>lay your hands on her, so that she may be made well and live.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he went with him.And a great crowd followed him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24385Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24385Q\"></sup>thronged about him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And there was a woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24386R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24386R\"></sup>who had had a discharge of blood for twelve years,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and who had suffered much under many physicians, and had spent all that she had, and was no better but rather grew worse.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She had heard the reports about Jesus and came up behind him in the crowd and touched his garment.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For she said, “If I touch even his garments, I will be made well.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24390S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24390S\"></sup>And immediately the flow of blood dried up, and she felt in her body that she was healed of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24390T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24390T\"></sup>disease.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And Jesus, perceiving in himself that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24391U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24391U\"></sup>power had gone out from him, immediately turned about in the crowd and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Who touched my garments?”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And his disciples said to him, “You see the crowd pressing around you, and yet you say, <span class=\"woj\">‘Who touched me?’</span>”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And he looked around to see who had done it.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But the woman, knowing what had happened to her, came in fear and trembling and fell down before him and told him the whole truth.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And he said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Daughter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24395V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24395V\"></sup>your faith has made you well; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24395W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24395W\"></sup>go in peace, and be healed of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24395X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24395X\"></sup>disease.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>While he was still speaking, there came from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24396Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24396Y\"></sup>the ruler's house some who said, “Your daughter is dead. Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24396Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24396Z\"></sup>trouble <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24396AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24396AA\"></sup>the Teacher any further?”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But overhearing what they said, Jesus said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24397AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24397AB\"></sup>the ruler of the synagogue, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not fear, only believe.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And he allowed no one to follow him except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24398AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24398AC\"></sup>Peter and James and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24398AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24398AD\"></sup>John the brother of James.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>They came to the house of the ruler of the synagogue, and Jesus saw a commotion, people weeping and wailing loudly.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And when he had entered, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24400AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24400AE\"></sup>“Why are you making a commotion and weeping? The child is not dead but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24400AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24400AF\"></sup>sleeping.”</span>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And they laughed at him. But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24401AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24401AG\"></sup>put them all outside and took the child's father and mother and those who were with him and went in where the child was.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24402AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24402AH\"></sup>Taking her by the hand he said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Talitha cumi,”</span> which means, <span class=\"woj\">“Little girl, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24402AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24402AI\"></sup>arise.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And immediately the girl got up and began walking (for she was twelve years of age), and they were immediately overcome with amazement.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24404AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24404AJ\"></sup>he strictly charged them that no one should know this, and told them to give her something to eat."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24405A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24405A\"></sup>He went away from there and came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24405B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24405B\"></sup>his hometown, and his disciples followed him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24406C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24406C\"></sup>on the Sabbath he began to teach in the synagogue, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24406D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24406D\"></sup>many who heard him were astonished, saying, “Where did this man get these things? What is the wisdom given to him? How are such mighty works done by his hands?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24407E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24407E\"></sup>Is not this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24407F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24407F\"></sup>the carpenter, the son of Mary and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24407G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24407G\"></sup>brother of James and Joses and Judas and Simon? And are not his sisters here with us?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24407H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24407H\"></sup>they took offense at him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24408I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24408I\"></sup>“A prophet is not without honor, except in his hometown and among his relatives and in his own household.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24409J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24409J\"></sup>he could do no mighty work there, except that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24409K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24409K\"></sup>he laid his hands on a few sick people and healed them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24410L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24410L\"></sup>he marveled because of their unbelief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24410M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24410M\"></sup>And he went about among the villages teaching.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24411N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24411N\"></sup>And he called the twelve and began to send them out two by two, and gave them authority over the unclean spirits.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He charged them to take nothing for their journey except a staff—no bread, no bag, no money in their belts—",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>but to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24413O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24413O\"></sup>wear sandals and not put on two tunics.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Whenever you enter a house, stay there until you depart from there.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And if any place will not receive you and they will not listen to you, when you leave, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24415P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24415P\"></sup>shake off the dust that is on your feet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24415Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24415Q\"></sup>as a testimony against them.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24416R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24416R\"></sup>So they went out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24416S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24416S\"></sup>proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24416T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24416T\"></sup>that people should repent.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24417U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24417U\"></sup>And they cast out many demons and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24417V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24417V\"></sup>anointed with oil many who were sick and healed them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24418W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24418W\"></sup>King Herod heard of it, for Jesus' name had become known. Some said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24418X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24418X\"></sup>“John the Baptist has been raised from the dead. That is why these miraculous powers are at work in him.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24419Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24419Y\"></sup>But others said, “He is Elijah.” And others said, “He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24419Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24419Z\"></sup>a prophet, like one of the prophets of old.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But when Herod heard of it, he said, “John, whom I beheaded, has been raised.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24421AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24421AA\"></sup>For it was Herod who had sent and seized John and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24421AB\"></sup>bound him in prison for the sake of Herodias, his brother Philip's wife, because he had married her.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24422AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24422AC\"></sup>For John had been saying to Herod, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24422AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24422AD\"></sup>“It is not lawful for you to have your brother's wife.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And Herodias had a grudge against him and wanted to put him to death. But she could not,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for Herod <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24424AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24424AE\"></sup>feared John, knowing that he was a righteous and holy man, and he kept him safe. When he heard him, he was greatly perplexed, and yet he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24424AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24424AF\"></sup>heard him gladly.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But an opportunity came when Herod <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24425AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24425AG\"></sup>on his birthday <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24425AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24425AH\"></sup>gave a banquet for his nobles and military commanders and the leading men of Galilee.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For when Herodias's daughter came in and danced, she pleased Herod and his guests. And the king said to the girl, “Ask me for whatever you wish, and I will give it to you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he vowed to her, “Whatever you ask me, I will give you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24427AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24427AI\"></sup>up to half of my kingdom.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And she went out and said to her mother, “For what should I ask?” And she said, “The head of John the Baptist.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And she came in immediately with haste to the king and asked, saying, “I want you to give me at once the head of John the Baptist on a platter.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And the king was exceedingly sorry, but because of his oaths and his guests he did not want to break his word to her.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And immediately the king sent an executioner with orders to bring John's head. He went and beheaded him in the prison",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and brought his head on a platter and gave it to the girl, and the girl gave it to her mother.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24433AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24433AJ\"></sup>disciples heard of it, they came and took his body and laid it in a tomb.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24434AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24434AK\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24434AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24434AL\"></sup>The apostles returned to Jesus and told him all that they had done and taught.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Come away by yourselves to a desolate place and rest a while.”</span> For many were coming and going, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24435AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24435AM\"></sup>they had no leisure even to eat.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24436AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24436AN\"></sup>And they went away in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24436AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24436AO\"></sup>the boat to a desolate place by themselves.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Now many saw them going and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24437AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24437AP\"></sup>recognized them, and they ran there on foot from all the towns and got there ahead of them.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When he went ashore he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24438AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24438AQ\"></sup>saw a great crowd, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24438AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24438AR\"></sup>he had compassion on them, because they were like sheep without a shepherd. And he began to teach them many things.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when it grew late, his disciples came to him and said, “This is a desolate place, and the hour is now late.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24440AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24440AS\"></sup>Send them away to go into the surrounding countryside and villages and buy themselves something to eat.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But he answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24441AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24441AT\"></sup>“You give them something to eat.”</span> And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24441AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24441AU\"></sup>they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24441AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24441AV\"></sup>“Shall we go and buy two hundred denarii worth of bread and give it to them to eat?”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“How many loaves do you have? Go and see.”</span> And when they had found out, they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24442AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24442AW\"></sup>“Five, and two fish.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Then he commanded them all to sit down in groups on the green grass.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So they sat down in groups, by hundreds and by fifties.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And taking the five loaves and the two fish, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24445AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24445AX\"></sup>looked up to heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24445AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24445AY\"></sup>said a blessing and broke the loaves and gave them to the disciples to set before the people. And he divided the two fish among them all.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And they all ate and were satisfied.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And they took up twelve baskets full of broken pieces and of the fish.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And those who ate the loaves were five thousand men.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24449AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24449AZ\"></sup>Immediately he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24449BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24449BA\"></sup>made his disciples get into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24449BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24449BB\"></sup>the boat and go before him to the other side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24449BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24449BC\"></sup>to Bethsaida, while he dismissed the crowd.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And after he had taken leave of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24450BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24450BD\"></sup>he went up on the mountain to pray.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24451BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24451BE\"></sup>evening came, the boat was out on the sea, and he was alone on the land.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And he saw that they were making headway painfully, for the wind was against them. And about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24452BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24452BF\"></sup>the fourth watch of the night he came to them, walking on the sea. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24452BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24452BG\"></sup>He meant to pass by them,",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>but when they saw him walking on the sea they thought it was a ghost, and cried out,",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>for they all saw him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24454BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24454BH\"></sup>were terrified. But immediately he spoke to them and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24454BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24454BI\"></sup>“Take heart; it is I. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24454BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24454BJ\"></sup>Do not be afraid.”</span>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And he got into the boat with them, and the wind ceased. And they were utterly astounded,",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24456BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24456BK\"></sup>they did not understand about the loaves, but their hearts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24456BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24456BL\"></sup>were hardened.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24457BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24457BM\"></sup>When they had crossed over, they came to land at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24457BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24457BN\"></sup>Gennesaret and moored to the shore.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>And when they got out of the boat, the people immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24458BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24458BO\"></sup>recognized him",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>and ran about the whole region and began to bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24459BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24459BP\"></sup>the sick people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24459BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24459BQ\"></sup>on their beds to wherever they heard he was.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And wherever he came, in villages, cities, or countryside, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24460BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24460BR\"></sup>they laid the sick in the marketplaces and implored him that they might touch even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24460BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24460BS\"></sup>the fringe of his garment. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24460BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24460BT\"></sup>as many as touched it were made well."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24461A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24461A\"></sup>Now when the Pharisees gathered to him, with some of the scribes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24461B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24461B\"></sup>who had come from Jerusalem,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>they saw that some of his disciples ate with hands that were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24462C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24462C\"></sup>defiled, that is, unwashed.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>(For the Pharisees and all the Jews do not eat unless they wash their hands properly, holding to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24463D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24463D\"></sup>the tradition of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24463E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24463E\"></sup>the elders,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and when they come from the marketplace, they do not eat unless they wash. And there are many other traditions that they observe, such as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24464F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24464F\"></sup>the washing of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24464G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24464G\"></sup>cups and pots and copper vessels and dining couches.)",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the Pharisees and the scribes asked him, “Why do your disciples not walk according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24465H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24465H\"></sup>the tradition of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24465I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24465I\"></sup>the elders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24465J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24465J\"></sup>but eat with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24465K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24465K\"></sup>defiled hands?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Well did Isaiah prophesy of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24466L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24466L\"></sup>hypocrites, as it is written,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24466M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24466M\"></sup>“‘This people honors me with their lips,</span><span class=\"woj\">but their heart is far from me;</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>in vain do they worship me,</span><span class=\"woj\">teaching as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24467N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24467N\"></sup>doctrines the commandments of men.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You leave the commandment of God and hold to the tradition of men.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You have a fine way of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24469O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24469O\"></sup>rejecting the commandment of God in order to establish your tradition!</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For Moses said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24470P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24470P\"></sup>‘Honor your father and your mother’; and, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24470Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24470Q\"></sup>‘Whoever reviles father or mother must surely die.’</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But you say, ‘If a man tells his father or his mother, “Whatever you would have gained from me is Corban”’ (that is, given to God)—</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>then you no longer permit him to do anything for his father or mother,</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24473R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24473R\"></sup>making void the word of God by your tradition that you have handed down. And many such things you do.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he called the people to him again and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24474S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24474S\"></sup>“Hear me, all of you, and understand:</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24475T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24475T\"></sup>There is nothing outside a person that by going into him can defile him, but the things that come out of a person are what defile him.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And when he had entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24476U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24476U\"></sup>the house and left the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24476V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24476V\"></sup>his disciples asked him about the parable.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24477W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24477W\"></sup>are you also without understanding? Do you not see that whatever goes into a person from outside cannot defile him,</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>since it enters not his heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24478X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24478X\"></sup>but his stomach, and is expelled?”</span> (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24478Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24478Y\"></sup>Thus he declared all foods clean.)",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24479Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24479Z\"></sup>“What comes out of a person is what defiles him.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For from within, out of the heart of man, come evil thoughts, sexual immorality, theft, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24480AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24480AA\"></sup>murder, adultery,</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>coveting, wickedness, deceit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24481AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24481AB\"></sup>sensuality, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24481AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24481AC\"></sup>envy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24481AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24481AD\"></sup>slander, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24481AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24481AE\"></sup>pride, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24481AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24481AF\"></sup>foolishness.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24482AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24482AG\"></sup>All these evil things come from within, and they defile a person.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And from there he arose and went away to the region of Tyre and Sidon. And he entered a house and did not want anyone to know, yet he could not be hidden.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But immediately a woman whose little daughter had an unclean spirit heard of him and came and fell down at his feet.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24485AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24485AH\"></sup>Now the woman was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24485AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24485AI\"></sup>Gentile, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24485AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24485AJ\"></sup>a Syrophoenician by birth. And she begged him to cast the demon out of her daughter.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Let the children be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24486AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24486AK\"></sup>fed first, for it is not right to take the children's bread and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24486AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24486AL\"></sup>throw it to the dogs.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But she answered him, “Yes, Lord; yet even the dogs under the table eat the children's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24487AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24487AM\"></sup>crumbs.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“For this statement you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24488AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24488AN\"></sup>go your way; the demon has left your daughter.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And she went home and found the child lying in bed and the demon gone.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24490AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24490AO\"></sup>Then he returned from the region of Tyre and went through Sidon to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24490AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24490AP\"></sup>the Sea of Galilee, in the region of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24490AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24490AQ\"></sup>Decapolis.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And they brought to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24491AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24491AR\"></sup>a man who was deaf and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24491AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24491AS\"></sup>had a speech impediment, and they begged him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24491AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24491AT\"></sup>lay his hand on him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24492AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24492AU\"></sup>taking him aside from the crowd privately, he put his fingers into his ears, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24492AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24492AV\"></sup>after spitting touched his tongue.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24493AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24493AW\"></sup>looking up to heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24493AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24493AX\"></sup>he sighed and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Ephphatha,”</span> that is, <span class=\"woj\">“Be opened.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24494AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24494AY\"></sup>And his ears were opened, his tongue was released, and he spoke plainly.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24495AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24495AZ\"></sup>Jesus charged them to tell no one. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24495BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24495BA\"></sup>the more he charged them, the more zealously they proclaimed it.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24496BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24496BB\"></sup>astonished beyond measure, saying, “He has done all things well. He even makes the deaf hear and the mute speak.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24497A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24497A\"></sup>In those days, when again a great crowd had gathered, and they had nothing to eat, he called his disciples to him and said to them,",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24498B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24498B\"></sup>“I have compassion on the crowd, because they have been with me now three days and have nothing to eat.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And if I send them away hungry to their homes, they will faint on the way. And some of them have come from far away.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And his disciples answered him, “How can one feed these people with bread here in this desolate place?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he asked them, <span class=\"woj\">“How many loaves do you have?”</span> They said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24501C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24501C\"></sup>“Seven.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he directed the crowd to sit down on the ground. And he took the seven loaves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24502D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24502D\"></sup>having given thanks, he broke them and gave them to his disciples to set before the people; and they set them before the crowd.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And they had a few small fish. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24503E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24503E\"></sup>having blessed them, he said that these also should be set before them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24504F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24504F\"></sup>they ate and were satisfied. And they took up the broken pieces left over, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24504G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24504G\"></sup>seven baskets full.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And there were about four thousand people. And he sent them away.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And immediately he got into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24506H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24506H\"></sup>the boat with his disciples and went to the district of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24506I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24506I\"></sup>Dalmanutha.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24507J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24507J\"></sup>The Pharisees came and began to argue with him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24507K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24507K\"></sup>seeking from him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24507L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24507L\"></sup>a sign from heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24507M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24507M\"></sup>to test him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24508N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24508N\"></sup>he sighed deeply <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24508O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24508O\"></sup>in his spirit and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Why does this generation seek a sign? Truly, I say to you, no sign will be given to this generation.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24509P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24509P\"></sup>he left them, got into the boat again, and went to the other side.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now they had forgotten to bring bread, and they had only one loaf with them in the boat.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he cautioned them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Watch out; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24511Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24511Q\"></sup>beware of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24511R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24511R\"></sup>the leaven of the Pharisees and the leaven of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24511S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24511S\"></sup>Herod.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they began discussing with one another the fact that they had no bread.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24513T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24513T\"></sup>Jesus, aware of this, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you discussing the fact that you have no bread? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24513U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24513U\"></sup>Do you not yet perceive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24513V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24513V\"></sup>or understand? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24513W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24513W\"></sup>Are your hearts hardened?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24514X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24514X\"></sup>Having eyes do you not see, and having ears do you not hear? And do you not remember?</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When I broke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24515Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24515Y\"></sup>the five loaves for the five thousand, how many baskets full of broken pieces did you take up?”</span> They said to him, “Twelve.”",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24516Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24516Z\"></sup>the seven for the four thousand, how many baskets full of broken pieces did you take up?”</span> And they said to him, “Seven.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you not yet understand?”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And they came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24518AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24518AA\"></sup>to Bethsaida. And some people brought to him a blind man and begged him to touch him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24519AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24519AB\"></sup>he took the blind man by the hand and led him out of the village, and when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24519AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24519AC\"></sup>he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24519AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24519AD\"></sup>spit on his eyes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24519AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24519AE\"></sup>laid his hands on him, he asked him, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you see anything?”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he looked up and said, “I see people, but they look like trees, walking.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then Jesus laid his hands on his eyes again; and he opened his eyes, his sight was restored, and he saw everything clearly.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And he sent him to his home, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24522AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24522AF\"></sup>“Do not even enter the village.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24523AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24523AG\"></sup>And Jesus went on with his disciples to the villages of Caesarea Philippi. And on the way he asked his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Who do people say that I am?”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And they told him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24524AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24524AH\"></sup>“John the Baptist; and others say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24524AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24524AI\"></sup>Elijah; and others, one of the prophets.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he asked them, <span class=\"woj\">“But who do you say that I am?”</span> Peter answered him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24525AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24525AJ\"></sup>“You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24525AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24525AK\"></sup>the Christ.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24526AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24526AL\"></sup>And he strictly charged them to tell no one about him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24527AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24527AM\"></sup>And he began to teach them that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24527AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24527AN\"></sup>the Son of Man must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24527AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24527AO\"></sup>suffer many things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24527AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24527AP\"></sup>be rejected by the elders and the chief priests and the scribes and be killed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24527AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24527AQ\"></sup>after three days rise again.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And he said this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24528AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24528AR\"></sup>plainly. And Peter took him aside and began to rebuke him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But turning and seeing his disciples, he rebuked Peter and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24529AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24529AS\"></sup>“Get behind me, Satan! For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24529AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24529AT\"></sup>are not setting your mind on the things of God, but on the things of man.”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And calling the crowd to him with his disciples, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“If anyone would come after me, let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24530AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24530AU\"></sup>deny himself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24530AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24530AV\"></sup>take up his cross and follow me.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24531AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24531AW\"></sup>whoever would save his life will lose it, but whoever loses his life for my sake <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24531AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24531AX\"></sup>and the gospel's will save it.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24532AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24532AY\"></sup>For what does it profit a man to gain the whole world and forfeit his soul?</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24533AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24533AZ\"></sup>what can a man give in return for his soul?</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24534BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24534BA\"></sup>whoever is ashamed of me and of my words in this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24534BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24534BB\"></sup>adulterous and sinful generation, of him will the Son of Man also be ashamed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24534BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24534BC\"></sup>when he comes in the glory of his Father with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24534BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24534BD\"></sup>the holy angels.”</span>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, there are some standing here who will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24535A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24535A\"></sup>taste death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24535B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24535B\"></sup>until they see the kingdom of God after it has come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24535C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24535C\"></sup>with power.”</span>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24536D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24536D\"></sup>And after six days Jesus took with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24536E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24536E\"></sup>Peter and James and John, and led them up a high mountain by themselves. And he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24536F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24536F\"></sup>transfigured before them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24537G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24537G\"></sup>his clothes became radiant, intensely white, as no one on earth could bleach them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And there appeared to them Elijah with Moses, and they were talking with Jesus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Peter said to Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24539H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24539H\"></sup>“Rabbi, it is good that we are here. Let us make three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24539I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24539I\"></sup>tents, one for you and one for Moses and one for Elijah.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24540J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24540J\"></sup>he did not know what to say, for they were terrified.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24541K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24541K\"></sup>a cloud overshadowed them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24541L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24541L\"></sup>a voice came out of the cloud, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24541M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24541M\"></sup>“This is my beloved Son; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24541N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24541N\"></sup>listen to him.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And suddenly, looking around, they no longer saw anyone with them but Jesus only.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24543O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24543O\"></sup>And as they were coming down the mountain, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24543P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24543P\"></sup>he charged them to tell no one what they had seen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24543Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24543Q\"></sup>until the Son of Man had risen from the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24544R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24544R\"></sup>So they kept the matter to themselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24544S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24544S\"></sup>questioning what this rising from the dead might mean.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they asked him, “Why do the scribes say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24545T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24545T\"></sup>that first Elijah must come?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Elijah does come first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24546U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24546U\"></sup>to restore all things. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24546V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24546V\"></sup>how is it written of the Son of Man that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24546W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24546W\"></sup>suffer many things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24546X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24546X\"></sup>be treated with contempt?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But I tell you that Elijah has come, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24547Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24547Y\"></sup>they did to him whatever they pleased, as it is written of him.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24548Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24548Z\"></sup>And when they came to the disciples, they saw a great crowd around them, and scribes arguing with them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And immediately all the crowd, when they saw him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24549AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24549AA\"></sup>were greatly amazed and ran up to him and greeted him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he asked them, <span class=\"woj\">“What are you arguing about with them?”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And someone from the crowd answered him, “Teacher, I brought my son to you, for he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24551AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24551AB\"></sup>a spirit that makes him mute.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And whenever it seizes him, it throws him down, and he foams and grinds his teeth and becomes rigid. So I asked your disciples to cast it out, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24552AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24552AC\"></sup>they were not able.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24553AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24553AD\"></sup>faithless generation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24553AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24553AE\"></sup>how long am I to be with you? How long am I to bear with you? Bring him to me.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And they brought the boy to him. And when the spirit saw him, immediately it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24554AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24554AF\"></sup>convulsed the boy, and he fell on the ground and rolled about, foaming at the mouth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Jesus asked his father, <span class=\"woj\">“How long has this been happening to him?”</span> And he said, “From childhood.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And it has often cast him into fire and into water, to destroy him. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24556AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24556AG\"></sup>if you can do anything, have compassion on us and help us.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24557AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24557AH\"></sup>“‘If you can’! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24557AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24557AI\"></sup>All things are possible for one who believes.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Immediately the father of the child cried out and said, “I believe; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24558AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24558AJ\"></sup>help my unbelief!”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And when Jesus saw that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24559AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24559AK\"></sup>a crowd came running together, he rebuked the unclean spirit, saying to it, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24559AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24559AL\"></sup>“You mute and deaf spirit, I command you, come out of him and never enter him again.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And after crying out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24560AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24560AM\"></sup>convulsing him terribly, it came out, and the boy was like a corpse, so that most of them said, “He is dead.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24561AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24561AN\"></sup>took him by the hand and lifted him up, and he arose.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And when he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24562AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24562AO\"></sup>entered the house, his disciples asked him privately, “Why could we not cast it out?”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“This kind cannot be driven out by anything but prayer.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24564AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24564AP\"></sup>They went on from there and passed through Galilee. And he did not want anyone to know,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>for he was teaching his disciples, saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“The Son of Man is going to be delivered into the hands of men, and they will kill him. And when he is killed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24565AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24565AQ\"></sup>after three days he will rise.”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24566AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24566AR\"></sup>But they did not understand the saying, and were afraid to ask him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24567AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24567AS\"></sup>they came to Capernaum. And when he was in the house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24567AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24567AT\"></sup>he asked them, <span class=\"woj\">“What were you discussing on the way?”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But they kept silent, for on the way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24568AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24568AU\"></sup>they had argued with one another about who was the greatest.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And he sat down and called the twelve. And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24569AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24569AV\"></sup>“If anyone would be first, he must be last of all and servant of all.”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And he took a child and put him in the midst of them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24570AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24570AW\"></sup>taking him in his arms, he said to them,",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24571AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24571AX\"></sup>“Whoever receives one such child in my name receives me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24571AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24571AY\"></sup>whoever receives me, receives not me but him who sent me.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24572AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24572AZ\"></sup>John said to him, “Teacher, we saw someone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24572BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24572BA\"></sup>casting out demons in your name, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24572BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24572BB\"></sup>we tried to stop him, because he was not following us.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not stop him, for no one who does a mighty work in my name will be able soon afterward to speak evil of me.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24574BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24574BC\"></sup>For the one who is not against us is for us.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>For truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24575BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24575BD\"></sup>whoever gives you a cup of water to drink because you belong to Christ will by no means lose his reward.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24576BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24576BE\"></sup>“Whoever causes one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24576BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24576BF\"></sup>these little ones who believe in me to sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24576BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24576BG\"></sup>it would be better for him if a great millstone were hung around his neck and he were thrown into the sea.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24577BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24577BH\"></sup>And if your hand causes you to sin, cut it off. It is better for you to enter life crippled than with two hands to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24577BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24577BI\"></sup>hell, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24577BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24577BJ\"></sup>the unquenchable fire.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24578BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24578BK\"></sup>And if your foot causes you to sin, cut it off. It is better for you to enter life lame than with two feet to be thrown into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24578BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24578BL\"></sup>hell.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24579BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24579BM\"></sup>And if your eye causes you to sin, tear it out. It is better for you to enter the kingdom of God with one eye than with two eyes to be thrown into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24579BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24579BN\"></sup>hell,</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>‘where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24580BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24580BO\"></sup>their worm does not die and the fire is not quenched.’</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>For everyone will be salted with fire.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24582BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24582BP\"></sup>Salt is good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24582BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24582BQ\"></sup>but if the salt has lost its saltiness, how will you make it salty again? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24582BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24582BR\"></sup>Have salt in yourselves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24582BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24582BS\"></sup>be at peace with one another.”</span>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24583A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24583A\"></sup>And he left there and went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24583B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24583B\"></sup>to the region of Judea and beyond the Jordan, and crowds gathered to him again. And again, as was his custom, he taught them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Pharisees came up and in order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24584C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24584C\"></sup>to test him asked, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24584D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24584D\"></sup>“Is it lawful for a man to divorce his wife?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“What did Moses command you?”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24586E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24586E\"></sup>“Moses allowed a man to write a certificate of divorce and to send her away.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Because of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24587F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24587F\"></sup>hardness of heart he wrote you this commandment.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24588G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24588G\"></sup>from the beginning of creation, ‘God made them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24588H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24588H\"></sup>male and female.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24589I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24589I\"></sup>‘Therefore a man shall leave his father and mother and hold fast to his wife,</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24590J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24590J\"></sup>the two shall become one flesh.’ So they are no longer two but one flesh.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24591K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24591K\"></sup>What therefore God has joined together, let not man separate.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And in the house the disciples asked him again about this matter.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24593L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24593L\"></sup>“Whoever divorces his wife and marries another commits adultery against her,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24594M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24594M\"></sup>if she divorces her husband and marries another, she commits adultery.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24595N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24595N\"></sup>And they were bringing children to him that he might touch them, and the disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24595O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24595O\"></sup>rebuked them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when Jesus saw it, he was indignant and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24596P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24596P\"></sup>“Let the children come to me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24596Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24596Q\"></sup>do not hinder them, for to such belongs the kingdom of God.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24597R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24597R\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, whoever does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24597S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24597S\"></sup>receive the kingdom of God like a child shall not enter it.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24598T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24598T\"></sup>he took them in his arms and blessed them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24598U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24598U\"></sup>laying his hands on them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24599V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24599V\"></sup>And as he was setting out on his journey, a man ran up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24599W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24599W\"></sup>knelt before him and asked him, “Good Teacher, what must I do to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24599X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24599X\"></sup>inherit eternal life?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you call me good? No one is good except God alone.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You know the commandments: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24601Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24601Y\"></sup>‘Do not murder, Do not commit adultery, Do not steal, Do not bear false witness, Do not defraud, Honor your father and mother.’”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he said to him, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24602Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24602Z\"></sup>all these I have kept from my youth.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24603AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24603AA\"></sup>looking at him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24603AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24603AB\"></sup>loved him, and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You lack one thing: go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24603AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24603AC\"></sup>sell all that you have and give to the poor, and you will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24603AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24603AD\"></sup>treasure in heaven; and come, follow me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24604AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24604AE\"></sup>Disheartened by the saying, he went away sorrowful, for he had great possessions.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24605AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24605AF\"></sup>looked around and said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24605AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24605AG\"></sup>“How difficult it will be for those who have wealth to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24605AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24605AH\"></sup>the kingdom of God!”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And the disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24606AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24606AI\"></sup>were amazed at his words. But Jesus said to them again, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24606AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24606AJ\"></sup>“Children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24606AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24606AK\"></sup>how difficult it is to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24606AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24606AL\"></sup>the kingdom of God!</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is easier for a camel to go through the eye of a needle than for a rich person to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24607AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24607AM\"></sup>the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And they were exceedingly astonished, and said to him, “Then who can be saved?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24609AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24609AN\"></sup>looked at them and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24609AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24609AO\"></sup>“With man it is impossible, but not with God. For all things are possible with God.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Peter began to say to him, “See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24610AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24610AP\"></sup>we have left everything and followed you.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24611AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24611AQ\"></sup>there is no one who has left house or brothers or sisters or mother or father or children or lands, for my sake and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24611AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24611AR\"></sup>for the gospel,</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>who will not receive a hundredfold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24612AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24612AS\"></sup>now in this time, houses and brothers and sisters and mothers and children and lands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24612AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24612AT\"></sup>with persecutions, and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24612AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24612AU\"></sup>the age to come eternal life.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24613AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24613AV\"></sup>many who are first will be last, and the last first.”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24614AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24614AW\"></sup>And they were on the road, going up to Jerusalem, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24614AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24614AX\"></sup>Jesus was walking ahead of them. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24614AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24614AY\"></sup>they were amazed, and those who followed were afraid. And taking the twelve again, he began to tell them what was to happen to him,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\">“See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24615AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24615AZ\"></sup>we are going up to Jerusalem, and the Son of Man will be delivered over to the chief priests and the scribes, and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24615BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24615BA\"></sup>condemn him to death and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24615BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24615BB\"></sup>deliver him over to the Gentiles.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24616BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24616BC\"></sup>mock him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24616BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24616BD\"></sup>spit on him, and flog him and kill him. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24616BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24616BE\"></sup>after three days he will rise.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24617BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24617BF\"></sup>And James and John, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24617BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24617BG\"></sup>the sons of Zebedee, came up to him and said to him, “Teacher, we want you to do for us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24617BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24617BH\"></sup>whatever we ask of you.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24618BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24618BI\"></sup>“What do you want me to do for you?”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And they said to him, “Grant us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24619BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24619BJ\"></sup>to sit, one at your right hand and one at your left, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24619BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24619BK\"></sup>in your glory.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24620BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24620BL\"></sup>“You do not know what you are asking. Are you able <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24620BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24620BM\"></sup>to drink the cup that I drink, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24620BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24620BN\"></sup>to be baptized with the baptism with which I am baptized?”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And they said to him, “We are able.” And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24621BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24621BO\"></sup>“The cup that I drink <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24621BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24621BP\"></sup>you will drink, and with the baptism with which I am baptized, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24621BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24621BQ\"></sup>you will be baptized,</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>but to sit at my right hand or at my left is not mine to grant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24622BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24622BR\"></sup>but it is for those for whom it has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24622BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24622BS\"></sup>prepared.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And when the ten heard it, they began to be indignant at James and John.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24624BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24624BT\"></sup>And Jesus called them to him and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You know that those who are considered rulers of the Gentiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24624BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24624BU\"></sup>lord it over them, and their great ones exercise authority over them.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24625BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24625BV\"></sup>it shall not be so among you. But whoever would be great among you must be your servant,</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>and whoever would be first among you must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24626BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24626BW\"></sup>slave of all.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>For even the Son of Man came not to be served but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24627BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24627BX\"></sup>to serve, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24627BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24627BY\"></sup>to give his life as a ransom for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24627BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24627BZ\"></sup>many.”</span>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24628CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24628CA\"></sup>And they came to Jericho. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24628CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24628CB\"></sup>as he was leaving Jericho with his disciples and a great crowd, Bartimaeus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24628CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24628CC\"></sup>a blind beggar, the son of Timaeus, was sitting by the roadside.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And when he heard that it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24629CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24629CD\"></sup>Jesus of Nazareth, he began to cry out and say, “Jesus, Son of David, have mercy on me!”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24630CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24630CE\"></sup>rebuked him, telling him to be silent. But he cried out all the more, “Son of David, have mercy on me!”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And Jesus stopped and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Call him.”</span> And they called the blind man, saying to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24631CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24631CF\"></sup>“Take heart. Get up; he is calling you.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And throwing off his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24632CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24632CG\"></sup>cloak, he sprang up and came to Jesus.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24633CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24633CH\"></sup>“What do you want me to do for you?”</span> And the blind man said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24633CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24633CI\"></sup>“Rabbi, let me recover my sight.”",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go your way; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24634CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24634CJ\"></sup>your faith has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24634CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24634CK\"></sup>made you well.”</span> And immediately he recovered his sight and followed him on the way."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24635A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24635A\"></sup>Now when they drew near to Jerusalem, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24635B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24635B\"></sup>Bethphage and Bethany, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24635C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24635C\"></sup>the Mount of Olives, Jesus sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24635D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24635D\"></sup>two of his disciples",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the village in front of you, and immediately as you enter it you will find a colt tied, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24636E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24636E\"></sup>on which no one has ever sat. Untie it and bring it.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone says to you, ‘Why are you doing this?’ say, ‘The Lord has need of it and will send it back here immediately.’”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And they went away and found a colt tied at a door outside in the street, and they untied it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And some of those standing there said to them, “What are you doing, untying the colt?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And they told them what Jesus had said, and they let them go.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And they brought the colt to Jesus and threw their cloaks on it, and he sat on it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24642F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24642F\"></sup>spread their cloaks on the road, and others spread leafy branches that they had cut from the fields.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And those who went before and those who followed were shouting, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24643G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24643G\"></sup>“Hosanna! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24643H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24643H\"></sup>Blessed is he who comes in the name of the Lord!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Blessed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24644I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24644I\"></sup>the coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24644J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24644J\"></sup>kingdom of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24644K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24644K\"></sup>our father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24644L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24644L\"></sup>David! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24644M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24644M\"></sup>Hosanna <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24644N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24644N\"></sup>in the highest!”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24645O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24645O\"></sup>And he entered Jerusalem and went into the temple. And when he had looked around at everything, as it was already late, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24645P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24645P\"></sup>he went out to Bethany with the twelve.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24646Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24646Q\"></sup>On the following day, when they came from Bethany, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24646R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24646R\"></sup>he was hungry.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24647S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24647S\"></sup>And seeing in the distance a fig tree in leaf, he went to see if he could find anything on it. When he came to it, he found nothing but leaves, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24647T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24647T\"></sup>it was not the season for figs.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he said to it, <span class=\"woj\">“May no one ever eat fruit from you again.”</span> And his disciples heard it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24649U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24649U\"></sup>And they came to Jerusalem. And he entered the temple and began to drive out those who sold and those who bought in the temple, and he overturned the tables of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24649V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24649V\"></sup>the money-changers and the seats of those who sold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24649W\"></sup>pigeons.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he would not allow anyone to carry anything through the temple.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And he was teaching them and saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Is it not written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24651X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24651X\"></sup>‘My house shall be called a house of prayer for all the nations’? But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24651Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24651Y\"></sup>you have made it a den of robbers.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the chief priests and the scribes heard it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24652Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24652Z\"></sup>were seeking a way to destroy him, for they feared him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24652AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24652AA\"></sup>all the crowd was astonished at his teaching.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24653AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24653AB\"></sup>And when evening came they went out of the city.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24654AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24654AC\"></sup>As they passed by in the morning, they saw the fig tree withered away to its roots.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Peter remembered and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24655AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24655AD\"></sup>“Rabbi, look! The fig tree that you cursed has withered.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24656AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24656AE\"></sup>faith in God.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24657AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24657AF\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, whoever says to this mountain, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24657AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24657AG\"></sup>‘Be taken up and thrown into the sea,’ and does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24657AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24657AH\"></sup>doubt in his heart, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24657AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24657AI\"></sup>believes that what he says will come to pass, it will be done for him.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24658AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24658AJ\"></sup>whatever you ask in prayer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24658AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24658AK\"></sup>believe that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24658AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24658AL\"></sup>have received it, and it will be yours.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And whenever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24659AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24659AM\"></sup>you stand praying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24659AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24659AN\"></sup>forgive, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24659AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24659AO\"></sup>if you have anything against anyone, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24659AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24659AP\"></sup>your Father also who is in heaven may forgive you your trespasses.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24660AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24660AQ\"></sup>And they came again to Jerusalem. And as he was walking in the temple, the chief priests and the scribes and the elders came to him,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24661AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24661AR\"></sup>“By what authority are you doing these things, or who gave you this authority to do them?”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I will ask you one question; answer me, and I will tell you by what authority I do these things.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Was the baptism of John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24663AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24663AS\"></sup>from heaven or from man? Answer me.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And they discussed it with one another, saying, “If we say, ‘From heaven,’ he will say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24664AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24664AT\"></sup>‘Why then did you not believe him?’",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But shall we say, ‘From man’?”—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24665AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24665AU\"></sup>they were afraid of the people, for they all held that John really was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24665AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24665AV\"></sup>a prophet.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So they answered Jesus, “We do not know.” And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Neither will I tell you by what authority I do these things.”</span>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24667A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24667A\"></sup>And he began to speak to them in parables. <span class=\"woj\">“A man planted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24667B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24667B\"></sup>a vineyard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24667C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24667C\"></sup>and put a fence around it and dug a pit for the winepress and built a tower, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24667D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24667D\"></sup>leased it to tenants and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24667E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24667E\"></sup>went into another country.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the season came, he sent a servant to the tenants to get from them some of the fruit of the vineyard.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24669F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24669F\"></sup>And they took him and beat him and sent him away empty-handed.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24670G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24670G\"></sup>Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24670H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24670H\"></sup>he sent to them another servant, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24670I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24670I\"></sup>they struck him on the head and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24670J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24670J\"></sup>treated him shamefully.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24671K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24671K\"></sup>And he sent another, and him they killed. And so with many others: some they beat, and some they killed.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He had still one other, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24672L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24672L\"></sup>a beloved son. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24672M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24672M\"></sup>Finally he sent him to them, saying, ‘They will respect my son.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But those tenants said to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24673N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24673N\"></sup>‘This is the heir. Come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24673O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24673O\"></sup>let us kill him, and the inheritance will be ours.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And they took him and killed him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24674P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24674P\"></sup>threw him out of the vineyard.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>What will the owner of the vineyard do? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24675Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24675Q\"></sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24675R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24675R\"></sup>come and destroy the tenants and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24675S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24675S\"></sup>give the vineyard to others.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24676T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24676T\"></sup>Have you not read <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24676U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24676U\"></sup>this Scripture:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24676V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24676V\"></sup>“‘The stone that the builders rejected</span><span class=\"woj\">has become the cornerstone;</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>this was the Lord's doing,</span><span class=\"woj\">and it is marvelous in our eyes’?”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24678W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24678W\"></sup>they were seeking to arrest him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24678X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24678X\"></sup>but feared the people, for they perceived that he had told the parable against them. So they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24678Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24678Y\"></sup>left him and went away.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24679Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24679Z\"></sup>And they sent to him some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24679AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24679AA\"></sup>the Pharisees and some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24679AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24679AB\"></sup>the Herodians, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24679AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24679AC\"></sup>trap him in his talk.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And they came and said to him, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24680AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24680AD\"></sup>we know that you are true and do not care about anyone's opinion. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24680AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24680AE\"></sup>you are not swayed by appearances, but truly teach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24680AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24680AF\"></sup>the way of God. Is it lawful to pay <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24680AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24680AG\"></sup>taxes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24680AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24680AH\"></sup>Caesar, or not? Should we pay them, or should we not?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But, knowing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24681AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24681AI\"></sup>their hypocrisy, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24681AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24681AJ\"></sup>put me to the test? Bring me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24681AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24681AK\"></sup>a denarius and let me look at it.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they brought one. And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Whose likeness and inscription is this?”</span> They said to him, “Caesar's.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24683AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24683AL\"></sup>“Render to Caesar the things that are Caesar's, and to God the things that are God's.”</span> And they marveled at him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24684AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24684AM\"></sup>Sadducees came to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24684AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24684AN\"></sup>who say that there is no resurrection. And they asked him a question, saying,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Teacher, Moses wrote for us that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24685AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24685AO\"></sup>if a man's brother dies and leaves a wife, but leaves no child, the man must take the widow and raise up offspring for his brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>There were seven brothers; the first took a wife, and when he died left no offspring.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the second took her, and died, leaving no offspring. And the third likewise.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And the seven left no offspring. Last of all the woman also died.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In the resurrection, when they rise again, whose wife will she be? For the seven had her as wife.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Is this not the reason you are wrong, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24690AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24690AP\"></sup>you know neither the Scriptures nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24690AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24690AQ\"></sup>the power of God?</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For when they rise from the dead, they neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24691AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24691AR\"></sup>marry nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24691AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24691AS\"></sup>are given in marriage, but are like angels in heaven.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And as for the dead being raised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24692AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24692AT\"></sup>have you not read in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24692AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24692AU\"></sup>the book of Moses, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24692AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24692AV\"></sup>the passage about the bush, how God spoke to him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24692AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24692AW\"></sup>‘I am the God of Abraham, and the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob’?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He is not God of the dead, but of the living. You are quite wrong.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24694AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24694AX\"></sup>And one of the scribes came up and heard them disputing with one another, and seeing that he answered them well, asked him, “Which commandment is the most important of all?”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“The most important is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24695AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24695AY\"></sup>‘Hear, O Israel: The Lord our God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24695AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24695AZ\"></sup>the Lord is one.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And you shall love the Lord your God with all your heart and with all your soul and with all your mind and with all your strength.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24697BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24697BA\"></sup>The second is this: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24697BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24697BB\"></sup>‘You shall love your neighbor as yourself.’ There is no other commandment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24697BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24697BC\"></sup>greater than these.”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And the scribe said to him, “You are right, Teacher. You have truly said that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24698BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24698BD\"></sup>he is one, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24698BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24698BE\"></sup>there is no other besides him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And to love him with all the heart and with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24699BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24699BF\"></sup>the understanding and with all the strength, and to love one's neighbor as oneself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24699BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24699BG\"></sup>is much more than all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24699BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24699BH\"></sup>whole burnt offerings and sacrifices.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And when Jesus saw that he answered wisely, he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You are not far from the kingdom of God.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24700BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24700BI\"></sup>And after that no one dared to ask him any more questions.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24701BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24701BJ\"></sup>And as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24701BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24701BK\"></sup>Jesus taught in the temple, he said, <span class=\"woj\">“How can the scribes say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24701BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24701BL\"></sup>the Christ is the son of David?</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>David himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24702BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24702BM\"></sup>in the Holy Spirit, declared,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24702BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24702BN\"></sup>“‘The Lord said to my Lord,</span><span class=\"woj\">“Sit at my right hand,</span><span class=\"woj\">until I put your enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24702BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24702BO\"></sup>under your feet.”’</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>David himself calls him Lord. So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24703BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24703BP\"></sup>how is he his son?”</span> And the great throng <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24703BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24703BQ\"></sup>heard him gladly.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24704BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24704BR\"></sup>And in his teaching he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Beware of the scribes, who like to walk around in long robes and like greetings in the marketplaces</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and have the best seats in the synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24705BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24705BS\"></sup>the places of honor at feasts,</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24706BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24706BT\"></sup>who devour widows' houses and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24706BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24706BU\"></sup>for a pretense make long prayers. They will receive the greater condemnation.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24707BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24707BV\"></sup>And he sat down opposite <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24707BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24707BW\"></sup>the treasury and watched the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24707BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24707BX\"></sup>putting money into the offering box. Many rich people put in large sums.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And a poor widow came and put in two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24708BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24708BY\"></sup>small copper coins, which make a penny.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And he called his disciples to him and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24709BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24709BZ\"></sup>this poor widow has put in more than all those who are contributing to the offering box.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>For they all contributed out of their abundance, but she out of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24710CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24710CA\"></sup>poverty has put in everything she had, all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24710CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24710CB\"></sup>she had to live on.”</span>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24711A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24711A\"></sup>And as he came out of the temple, one of his disciples said to him, “Look, Teacher, what wonderful stones and what wonderful buildings!”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you see these great buildings? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24712B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24712B\"></sup>There will not be left here one stone upon another that will not be thrown down.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And as he sat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24713C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24713C\"></sup>the Mount of Olives opposite the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24713D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24713D\"></sup>Peter and James and John and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24713E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24713E\"></sup>Andrew asked him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24713F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24713F\"></sup>privately,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Tell us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24714G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24714G\"></sup>when will these things be, and what will be the sign when all these things are about to be accomplished?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Jesus began to say to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24715H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24715H\"></sup>“See that no one leads you astray.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24716I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24716I\"></sup>Many will come in my name, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24716J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24716J\"></sup>‘I am he!’ and they will lead many astray.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when you hear of wars and rumors of wars, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24717K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24717K\"></sup>do not be alarmed. This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24717L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24717L\"></sup>must take place, but the end is not yet.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24718M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24718M\"></sup>nation will rise against nation, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24718N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24718N\"></sup>kingdom against kingdom. There will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24718O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24718O\"></sup>earthquakes in various places; there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24718P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24718P\"></sup>famines. These are but the beginning of the birth pains.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24719Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24719Q\"></sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24719R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24719R\"></sup>be on your guard. For they will deliver you over to councils, and you will be beaten <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24719S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24719S\"></sup>in synagogues, and you will stand before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24719T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24719T\"></sup>governors and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24719U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24719U\"></sup>kings for my sake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24719V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24719V\"></sup>to bear witness before them.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the gospel must first be proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24720W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24720W\"></sup>to all nations.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And when they bring you to trial and deliver you over, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24721X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24721X\"></sup>do not be anxious beforehand what you are to say, but say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24721Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24721Y\"></sup>whatever is given you in that hour, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24721Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24721Z\"></sup>for it is not you who speak, but the Holy Spirit.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24722AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24722AA\"></sup>And brother will deliver brother over to death, and the father his child, and children will rise against parents and have them put to death.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24723AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24723AB\"></sup>And you will be hated by all for my name's sake. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24723AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24723AC\"></sup>But the one who endures to the end will be saved.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“But when you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24724AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24724AD\"></sup>the abomination of desolation standing where he ought not to be (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24724AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24724AE\"></sup>let the reader understand), then let those who are in Judea flee to the mountains.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24725AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24725AF\"></sup>Let the one who is on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24725AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24725AG\"></sup>the housetop not go down, nor enter his house, to take anything out,</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and let the one who is in the field not turn back to take his cloak.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24727AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24727AH\"></sup>alas for women who are pregnant and for those who are nursing infants in those days!</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Pray that it may not happen in winter.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For in those days there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24729AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24729AI\"></sup>such <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24729AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24729AJ\"></sup>tribulation as has not been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24729AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24729AK\"></sup>from the beginning of the creation that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24729AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24729AL\"></sup>God created until now, and never will be.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And if the Lord had not cut short the days, no human being would be saved. But for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24730AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24730AM\"></sup>the sake of the elect, whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24730AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24730AN\"></sup>he chose, he shortened the days.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24731AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24731AO\"></sup>then if anyone says to you, ‘Look, here is the Christ!’ or ‘Look, there he is!’ do not believe it.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24732AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24732AP\"></sup>For false christs and false prophets will arise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24732AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24732AQ\"></sup>perform signs and wonders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24732AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24732AR\"></sup>to lead astray, if possible, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24732AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24732AS\"></sup>the elect.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24733AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24733AT\"></sup>be on guard; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24733AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24733AU\"></sup>I have told you all things beforehand.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But in those days, after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24734AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24734AV\"></sup>that tribulation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24734AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24734AW\"></sup>the sun will be darkened, and the moon will not give its light,</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24735AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24735AX\"></sup>the stars will be falling from heaven, and the powers in the heavens will be shaken.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And then they will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24736AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24736AY\"></sup>the Son of Man coming in clouds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24736AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24736AZ\"></sup>with great power and glory.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24737BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24737BA\"></sup>he will send out the angels and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24737BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24737BB\"></sup>gather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24737BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24737BC\"></sup>his elect from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24737BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24737BD\"></sup>the four winds, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24737BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24737BE\"></sup>the ends of the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24737BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24737BF\"></sup>to the ends of heaven.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“From the fig tree learn its lesson: as soon as its branch becomes tender and puts out its leaves, you know that summer is near.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So also, when you see these things taking place, you know that he is near, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24739BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24739BG\"></sup>at the very gates.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24740BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24740BH\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, this generation will not pass away until all these things take place.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24741BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24741BI\"></sup>Heaven and earth will pass away, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24741BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24741BJ\"></sup>my words will not pass away.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“But concerning that day or that hour, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24742BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24742BK\"></sup>no one knows, not even the angels in heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24742BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24742BL\"></sup>nor the Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24742BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24742BM\"></sup>but only the Father.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24743BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24743BN\"></sup>Be on guard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24743BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24743BO\"></sup>keep awake. For you do not know when the time will come.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24744BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24744BP\"></sup>It is like a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24744BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24744BQ\"></sup>going on a journey, when he leaves home and puts his servants in charge, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24744BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24744BR\"></sup>each with his work, and commands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24744BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24744BS\"></sup>the doorkeeper to stay awake.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24745BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24745BT\"></sup>Therefore stay awake—for you do not know when the master of the house will come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24745BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24745BU\"></sup>in the evening, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24745BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24745BV\"></sup>at midnight, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24745BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24745BW\"></sup>when the rooster crows, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24745BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24745BX\"></sup>in the morning—</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>lest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24746BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24746BY\"></sup>he come suddenly and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24746BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24746BZ\"></sup>find you asleep.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And what I say to you I say to all: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24747CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24747CA\"></sup>Stay awake.”</span>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24748A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24748A\"></sup>It was now two days before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24748B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24748B\"></sup>the Passover and the Feast of Unleavened Bread. And the chief priests and the scribes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24748C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24748C\"></sup>were seeking how to arrest him by stealth and kill him,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for they said, “Not during the feast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24749D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24749D\"></sup>lest there be an uproar from the people.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24750E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24750E\"></sup>And while he was at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24750F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24750F\"></sup>Bethany in the house of Simon the leper, as he was reclining at table, a woman came with an alabaster flask of ointment of pure nard, very costly, and she broke the flask and poured it over his head.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>There were some who said to themselves indignantly, “Why was the ointment wasted like that?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For this ointment could have been sold for more than three hundred denarii and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24752G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24752G\"></sup>given to the poor.” And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24752H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24752H\"></sup>scolded her.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Leave her alone. Why do you trouble her? She has done a beautiful thing to me.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24754I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24754I\"></sup>you always have the poor with you, and whenever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24754J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24754J\"></sup>you want, you can do good for them. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24754K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24754K\"></sup>you will not always have me.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24755L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24755L\"></sup>She has done what she could; she has anointed my body beforehand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24755M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24755M\"></sup>for burial.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And truly, I say to you, wherever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24756N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24756N\"></sup>the gospel is proclaimed in the whole world, what she has done will be told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24756O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24756O\"></sup>in memory of her.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24757P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24757P\"></sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24757Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24757Q\"></sup>Judas Iscariot, who was one of the twelve, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24757R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24757R\"></sup>went to the chief priests in order to betray him to them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And when they heard it, they were glad and promised to give him money. And he sought an opportunity to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24758S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24758S\"></sup>betray him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24759T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24759T\"></sup>And on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24759U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24759U\"></sup>the first day of Unleavened Bread, when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24759V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24759V\"></sup>sacrificed the Passover lamb, his disciples said to him, “Where will you have us go and prepare for you to eat the Passover?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24760W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24760W\"></sup>two of his disciples and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the city, and a man carrying a jar of water will meet you. Follow him,</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and wherever he enters, say to the master of the house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24761X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24761X\"></sup>‘The Teacher says, Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24761Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24761Y\"></sup>my guest room, where I may eat the Passover with my disciples?’</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he will show you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24762Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24762Z\"></sup>a large upper room furnished and ready; there prepare for us.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the disciples set out and went to the city and found it just as he had told them, and they prepared the Passover.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24764AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24764AA\"></sup>And when it was evening, he came with the twelve.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And as they were reclining at table and eating, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24765AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24765AB\"></sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, one of you will betray me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24765AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24765AC\"></sup>one who is eating with me.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They began to be sorrowful and to say to him one after another, “Is it I?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24767AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24767AD\"></sup>one of the twelve, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24767AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24767AE\"></sup>one who is dipping bread into the dish with me.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the Son of Man goes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24768AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24768AF\"></sup>as it is written of him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24768AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24768AG\"></sup>woe to that man by whom the Son of Man is betrayed! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24768AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24768AH\"></sup>It would have been better for that man if he had not been born.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24769AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24769AI\"></sup>And as they were eating, he took bread, and after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24769AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24769AJ\"></sup>blessing it broke it and gave it to them, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Take; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24769AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24769AK\"></sup>this is my body.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he took a cup, and when he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24770AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24770AL\"></sup>given thanks he gave it to them, and they all drank of it.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24771AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24771AM\"></sup>“This is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24771AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24771AN\"></sup>blood of the covenant, which is poured out for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24771AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24771AO\"></sup>many.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Truly, I say to you, I will not drink again of the fruit of the vine until that day when I drink it new in the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24773AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24773AP\"></sup>And when they had sung a hymn, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24773AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24773AQ\"></sup>they went out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24773AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24773AR\"></sup>the Mount of Olives.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You will all fall away, for it is written, ‘I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24774AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24774AS\"></sup>strike the shepherd, and the sheep will be scattered.’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But after I am raised up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24775AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24775AT\"></sup>I will go before you to Galilee.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24776AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24776AU\"></sup>Peter said to him, “Even though they all fall away, I will not.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24777AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24777AV\"></sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I tell you, this very night, before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24777AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24777AW\"></sup>the rooster crows twice, you will deny me three times.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24778AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24778AX\"></sup>he said emphatically, “If I must die with you, I will not deny you.” And they all said the same.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24779AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24779AY\"></sup>And they went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24779AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24779AZ\"></sup>to a place called Gethsemane. And he said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Sit here while I pray.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And he took with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24780BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24780BA\"></sup>Peter and James and John, and began <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24780BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24780BB\"></sup>to be greatly distressed and troubled.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24781BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24781BC\"></sup>“My soul is very sorrowful, even to death. Remain here and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24781BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24781BD\"></sup>watch.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And going a little farther, he fell on the ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24782BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24782BE\"></sup>and prayed that, if it were possible, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24782BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24782BF\"></sup>the hour might pass from him.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24783BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24783BG\"></sup>“Abba, Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24783BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24783BH\"></sup>all things are possible for you. Remove <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24783BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24783BI\"></sup>this cup from me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24783BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24783BJ\"></sup>Yet not what I will, but what you will.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And he came and found them sleeping, and he said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, are you asleep? Could you not watch one hour?</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24785BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24785BK\"></sup>Watch and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24785BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24785BL\"></sup>pray that you may not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24785BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24785BM\"></sup>enter into temptation. The spirit indeed is willing, but the flesh is weak.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And again he went away and prayed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24786BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24786BN\"></sup>saying the same words.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And again he came and found them sleeping, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24787BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24787BO\"></sup>their eyes were very heavy, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24787BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24787BP\"></sup>they did not know what to answer him.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And he came the third time and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you still sleeping and taking your rest? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24788BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24788BQ\"></sup>It is enough; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24788BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24788BR\"></sup>the hour has come. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24788BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24788BS\"></sup>The Son of Man is betrayed into the hands of sinners.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Rise, let us be going; see, my betrayer is at hand.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24790BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24790BT\"></sup>And immediately, while he was still speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24790BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24790BU\"></sup>Judas came, one of the twelve, and with him a crowd with swords and clubs, from the chief priests and the scribes and the elders.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Now the betrayer had given them a sign, saying, “The one I will kiss is the man. Seize him and lead him away under guard.”",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And when he came, he went up to him at once and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24792BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24792BV\"></sup>“Rabbi!” And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24792BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24792BW\"></sup>kissed him.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And they laid hands on him and seized him.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>But one of those who stood by drew his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24794BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24794BX\"></sup>sword and struck the servant of the high priest and cut off his ear.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you come out as against a robber, with swords and clubs to capture me?</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24796BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24796BY\"></sup>Day after day I was with you in the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24796BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24796BZ\"></sup>teaching, and you did not seize me. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24796CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24796CA\"></sup>let the Scriptures be fulfilled.”</span>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24797CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24797CB\"></sup>And they all left him and fled.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And a young man followed him, with nothing but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24798CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24798CC\"></sup>a linen cloth about his body. And they seized him,",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>but he left the linen cloth and ran away naked.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24800CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24800CD\"></sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24800CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24800CE\"></sup>they led Jesus to the high priest. And all the chief priests and the elders and the scribes came together.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24801CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24801CF\"></sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24801CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24801CG\"></sup>Peter had followed him at a distance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24801CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24801CH\"></sup>right into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24801CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24801CI\"></sup>the courtyard of the high priest. And he was sitting with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24801CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24801CJ\"></sup>the guards and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24801CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24801CK\"></sup>warming himself at the fire.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>Now the chief priests and the whole council were seeking testimony against Jesus to put him to death, but they found none.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24803CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24803CL\"></sup>For many bore false witness against him, but their testimony <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24803CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24803CM\"></sup>did not agree.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>And some stood up and bore false witness against him, saying,",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24805CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24805CN\"></sup>“We heard him say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24805CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24805CO\"></sup>‘I will destroy this temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24805CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24805CP\"></sup>that is made with hands, and in three days I will build another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24805CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24805CQ\"></sup>not made with hands.’”",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>Yet even about this their testimony did not agree.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>And the high priest stood up in the midst and asked Jesus, “Have you no answer to make? What is it that these men testify against you?”",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24808CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24808CR\"></sup>he remained silent and made no answer. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24808CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24808CS\"></sup>Again the high priest asked him, “Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24808CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24808CT\"></sup>the Christ, the Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24808CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24808CU\"></sup>the Blessed?”",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“I am, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24809CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24809CV\"></sup>you will see the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24809CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24809CW\"></sup>seated at the right hand of Power, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24809CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24809CX\"></sup>coming with the clouds of heaven.”</span>",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>And the high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24810CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24810CY\"></sup>tore his garments and said, “What further witnesses do we need?",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>You have heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24811CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24811CZ\"></sup>his blasphemy. What is your decision?” And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24811DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24811DA\"></sup>all condemned him as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24811DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24811DB\"></sup>deserving death.",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24812DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24812DC\"></sup>And some began <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24812DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24812DD\"></sup>to spit on him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24812DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24812DE\"></sup>to cover his face and to strike him, saying to him, “Prophesy!” And the guards received him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24812DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24812DF\"></sup>with blows.",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24813DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24813DG\"></sup>And as Peter was below in the courtyard, one of the servant girls of the high priest came,",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup>and seeing Peter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24814DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24814DH\"></sup>warming himself, she looked at him and said, “You also were with the Nazarene, Jesus.”",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup>But he denied it, saying, “I neither know nor understand what you mean.” And he went out into the gateway and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24815DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24815DI\"></sup>the rooster crowed.",
			"69": "<sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup>And the servant girl saw him and began again to say to the bystanders, “This man is one of them.”",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup>But again he denied it. And after a little while the bystanders again said to Peter, “Certainly you are one of them, for you are a Galilean.”",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup>But he began to invoke a curse on himself and to swear, “I do not know this man of whom you speak.”",
			"72": "<sup class=\"versenum\">72 </sup>And immediately the rooster crowed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24819DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24819DJ\"></sup>a second time. And Peter remembered how Jesus had said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24819DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24819DK\"></sup>“Before the rooster crows twice, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24819DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24819DL\"></sup>deny me three times.”</span> And he broke down and wept."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24820A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24820A\"></sup>And as soon as it was morning, the chief priests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24820B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24820B\"></sup>held a consultation with the elders and scribes and the whole council. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24820C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24820C\"></sup>they bound Jesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24820D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24820D\"></sup>led him away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24820E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24820E\"></sup>delivered him over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24820F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24820F\"></sup>Pilate.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24821G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24821G\"></sup>And Pilate asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24821H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24821H\"></sup>“Are you the King of the Jews?” And he answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24821I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24821I\"></sup>“You have said so.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the chief priests accused him of many things.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Pilate again asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24823J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24823J\"></sup>“Have you no answer to make? See how many charges they bring against you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24824K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24824K\"></sup>made no further answer, so that Pilate was amazed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24825L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24825L\"></sup>Now at the feast he used to release for them one prisoner for whom they asked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And among the rebels in prison, who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24826M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24826M\"></sup>committed murder <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24826N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24826N\"></sup>in the insurrection, there was a man called Barabbas.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the crowd came up and began to ask Pilate to do as he usually did for them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he answered them, saying, “Do you want me to release for you the King of the Jews?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For he perceived that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24829O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24829O\"></sup>it was out of envy that the chief priests had delivered him up.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the chief priests stirred up the crowd to have him release for them Barabbas instead.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And Pilate again said to them, “Then what shall I do with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24831P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24831P\"></sup>the man you call the King of the Jews?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And they cried out again, “Crucify him.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And Pilate said to them, “Why? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24833Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24833Q\"></sup>What evil has he done?” But they shouted all the more, “Crucify him.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So Pilate, wishing to satisfy the crowd, released for them Barabbas, and having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24834R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24834R\"></sup>scourged Jesus, he delivered him to be crucified.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24835S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24835S\"></sup>And the soldiers led him away inside <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24835T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24835T\"></sup>the palace (that is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24835U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24835U\"></sup>the governor's headquarters), and they called together the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24835V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24835V\"></sup>battalion.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they clothed him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24836W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24836W\"></sup>a purple cloak, and twisting together a crown of thorns, they put it on him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And they began to salute him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24837X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24837X\"></sup>“Hail, King of the Jews!”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they were striking his head with a reed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24838Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24838Y\"></sup>spitting on him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24838Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24838Z\"></sup>kneeling down in homage to him.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24839AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24839AA\"></sup>mocked him, they stripped him of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24839AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24839AB\"></sup>the purple cloak and put his own clothes on him. And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24839AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24839AC\"></sup>led him out to crucify him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24840AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24840AD\"></sup>And they compelled a passerby, Simon of Cyrene, who was coming in from the country, the father of Alexander and Rufus, to carry his cross.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24841AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24841AE\"></sup>And they brought him to the place called Golgotha (which means Place of a Skull).",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And they offered him wine mixed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24842AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24842AF\"></sup>myrrh, but he did not take it.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they crucified him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24843AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24843AG\"></sup>divided his garments among them, casting lots for them, to decide what each should take.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24844AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24844AH\"></sup>it was the third hour when they crucified him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And the inscription of the charge against him read, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24845AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24845AI\"></sup>“The King of the Jews.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And with him they crucified two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24846AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24846AJ\"></sup>robbers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24846AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24846AK\"></sup>one on his right and one on his left.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24847AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24847AL\"></sup>those who passed by derided him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24847AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24847AM\"></sup>wagging their heads and saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24847AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24847AN\"></sup>“Aha! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24847AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24847AO\"></sup>You who would destroy the temple and rebuild it in three days,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>save yourself, and come down from the cross!”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So also the chief priests with the scribes mocked him to one another, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24849AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24849AP\"></sup>“He saved others; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24849AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24849AQ\"></sup>he cannot save himself.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24850AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24850AR\"></sup>the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24850AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24850AS\"></sup>the King of Israel, come down now from the cross that we may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24850AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24850AT\"></sup>see and believe.” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24850AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24850AU\"></sup>Those who were crucified with him also reviled him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And when the sixth hour had come, there was darkness over the whole land until the ninth hour.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And at the ninth hour Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24852AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24852AV\"></sup>cried with a loud voice, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24852AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24852AW\"></sup>“Eloi, Eloi, lema sabachthani?”</span> which means, <span class=\"woj\">“My God, my God, why have you forsaken me?”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And some of the bystanders hearing it said, “Behold, he is calling Elijah.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And someone ran and filled a sponge with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24854AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24854AX\"></sup>sour wine, put it on a reed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24854AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24854AY\"></sup>and gave it to him to drink, saying, “Wait, let us see whether Elijah will come to take him down.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24855AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24855AZ\"></sup>uttered a loud cry and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24855BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24855BA\"></sup>breathed his last.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24856BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24856BB\"></sup>the curtain of the temple was torn in two, from top to bottom.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24857BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24857BC\"></sup>And when the centurion, who stood facing him, saw that in this way he breathed his last, he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24857BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24857BD\"></sup>“Truly this man was the Son of God!”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>There were also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24858BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24858BE\"></sup>women looking on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24858BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24858BF\"></sup>from a distance, among whom were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24858BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24858BG\"></sup>Mary Magdalene, and Mary the mother of James the younger and of Joses, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24858BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24858BH\"></sup>Salome.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>When he was in Galilee, they followed him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24859BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24859BI\"></sup>ministered to him, and there were also many other women who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24859BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24859BJ\"></sup>came up with him to Jerusalem.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24860BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24860BK\"></sup>And when evening had come, since it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24860BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24860BL\"></sup>the day of Preparation, that is, the day before the Sabbath,",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Joseph of Arimathea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24861BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24861BM\"></sup>a respected member of the council, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24861BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24861BN\"></sup>was also himself looking for the kingdom of God, took courage and went to Pilate and asked for the body of Jesus.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Pilate was surprised to hear that he should have already died. And summoning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24862BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24862BO\"></sup>the centurion, he asked him whether he was already dead.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And when he learned from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24863BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24863BP\"></sup>the centurion that he was dead, he granted the corpse to Joseph.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And Joseph bought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24864BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24864BQ\"></sup>a linen shroud, and taking him down, wrapped him in the linen shroud and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24864BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24864BR\"></sup>laid him in a tomb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24864BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24864BS\"></sup>that had been cut out of the rock. And he rolled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24864BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24864BT\"></sup>a stone against the entrance of the tomb.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24865BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24865BU\"></sup>Mary Magdalene and Mary the mother of Joses saw where he was laid."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24866A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24866A\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24866B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24866B\"></sup>When the Sabbath was past, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24866C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24866C\"></sup>Mary Magdalene, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24866D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24866D\"></sup>Mary the mother of James, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24866E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24866E\"></sup>Salome <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24866F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24866F\"></sup>bought spices, so that they might go and anoint him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And very early on the first day of the week, when the sun had risen, they went to the tomb.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they were saying to one another, “Who will roll away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24868G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24868G\"></sup>the stone for us from the entrance of the tomb?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And looking up, they saw that the stone had been rolled back—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24869H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24869H\"></sup>it was very large.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24870I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24870I\"></sup>entering the tomb, they saw a young man sitting on the right side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24870J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24870J\"></sup>dressed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24870K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24870K\"></sup>a white robe, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24870L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24870L\"></sup>they were alarmed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24871M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24871M\"></sup>“Do not be alarmed. You seek Jesus of Nazareth, who was crucified. He has risen; he is not here. See the place where they laid him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But go, tell his disciples and Peter that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24872N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24872N\"></sup>he is going before you to Galilee. There you will see him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24872O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24872O\"></sup>just as he told you.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And they went out and fled from the tomb, for trembling and astonishment had seized them, and they said nothing to anyone, for they were afraid.[Some of the earliest manuscripts do not include 16:9–20.]",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>[[Now when he rose early on the first day of the week, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24874P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24874P\"></sup>he appeared first to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24874Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24874Q\"></sup>Mary Magdalene, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24874R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24874R\"></sup>from whom he had cast out seven demons.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24875S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24875S\"></sup>She went and told those who had been with him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24875T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24875T\"></sup>as they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24875U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24875U\"></sup>mourned and wept.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when they heard that he was alive and had been seen by her, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24876V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24876V\"></sup>would not believe it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24877W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24877W\"></sup>After these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24877X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24877X\"></sup>he appeared in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24877Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24877Y\"></sup>another form to two of them, as they were walking into the country.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24878Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24878Z\"></sup>And they went back and told the rest, but they did not believe them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Afterward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24879AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24879AA\"></sup>he appeared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24879AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24879AB\"></sup>to the eleven themselves as they were reclining at table, and he rebuked them for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24879AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24879AC\"></sup>unbelief and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24879AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24879AD\"></sup>hardness of heart, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24879AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24879AE\"></sup>they had not believed those who saw him after he had risen.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24880AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24880AF\"></sup>“Go into all the world and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24880AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24880AG\"></sup>proclaim the gospel to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24880AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24880AH\"></sup>the whole creation.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24881AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24881AI\"></sup>Whoever believes and is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24881AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24881AJ\"></sup>baptized <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24881AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24881AK\"></sup>will be saved, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24881AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24881AL\"></sup>whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24881AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24881AM\"></sup>does not believe will be condemned.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24882AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24882AN\"></sup>these signs will accompany those who believe: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24882AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24882AO\"></sup>in my name they will cast out demons; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24882AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24882AP\"></sup>they will speak in new tongues;</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24883AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24883AQ\"></sup>they will pick up serpents with their hands; and if they drink any deadly poison, it will not hurt them; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24883AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24883AR\"></sup>they will lay their hands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24883AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24883AS\"></sup>on the sick, and they will recover.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So then the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24884AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24884AT\"></sup>after he had spoken to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24884AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24884AU\"></sup>was taken up into heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24884AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24884AV\"></sup>sat down at the right hand of God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And they went out and preached everywhere, while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24885AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24885AW\"></sup>the Lord worked with them and confirmed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24885AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24885AX\"></sup>the message <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24885AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24885AY\"></sup>by accompanying signs.]]"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;